data.description: Amazing GOLF COURSE home in desirable Whitewater Creek. This 6 bedroom 3.5 bathroom home is located on a cul de sac lot on the 6th hole of Whitewater Creek Golf Course. Beautiful features include a wood paneled office/bedroom, formal dining room, breakfast area with a view, 3 car garage, a ton of storage and so much living space on the main level. Master Suite on the main level. Incredible must see finished back patio with fireplace, grilling area, island to gather and plenty of space to entertain. Enjoy the outdoors on the game day porch.
